description:
Recently sold: $216,000. Update listed through realtor link is below: Charming farm house with quaint setting.  3 br with huge walk in closets for each bedroom, master has two walkin closets. With an ensuite bathroom7'6"x11' with slipper claw foot tub.  Large LR and DR with built In desk area. Updated kitchen and bathrooms in 2006. Large sun porch. Dual fuel heat, peak shave hot water with high efficient Marathon unit.  Recently inspected and approved mound septic system. Must see to appreciate.  Large yard with plenty of space for parking toys, trailers, open spaces for games, no close neighbors to worry about. 
Roof and most windows replaced in 2007. 
underground power to both garages and to house with updated 200 amp service with generator bypass panel on pole.  Kitchen/baths have been rewired with GFI outlets.  Integrated fire detectors. Beautiful laundry room/basement bathroom combo. with laundry sorting area that is awesome for sorting.
If storage is what you need, this house has it.  Rock basement. Wonderfull well water. Many mature Lilacs, crab apples trees, Juneberries, Plumbs, lots of useable land. with room for animals if you desire, there is a chicken coop and fence.  Close to everything on the range.
